---
title: Weeknight Fragrant Hoisin Beef Noodles with Carrot, Onion, Green Beans and Peanuts
description: Perfect for a midweek meal, these Weeknight Fragrant Hoisin Beef Noodles can be on your table in less than 25 minutes.  Hoisin contains Chinese Five Spice, rice vinegar and red miso which gives it its delicious sweet-umami flavour.
